title: Casual Flex/Norms, gold+
body:
Took a break from the game over the summer holidays and need some new friends to play with. Have been plat for the past 4 seasons, but not looking to play solo queue for a bit. 

No flame and some maturity appreciated.

replies.body:
I hear your call from across the Oce Region and Reply with...
Your Welcome to join my Discord and meet the Friends, Handful of Active players and will expand quite shortly. 
I'm a sup main but can play any role required.
Add me and Request Discord if you are interested, Age 18+ Matured with an exception of Friends of Friends.
I hope to see you soon{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
